Package com.phasmidsoftware.dsaipg.adt.bqs

Class Stack_LinkedList<Item>

java.lang.Object
com.phasmidsoftware.dsaipg.adt.bqs.Stack_LinkedList<Item>
Type Parameters:
Item - the type of elements stored in this stack
All Implemented Interfaces:
Stack<Item>, Iterable<Item>
public class Stack_LinkedList<Item> extends Object implements Stack<Item>
Stack_LinkedList is a generic implementation of the Stack interface backed by a linked list. It provides operations to push, pop, and peek elements, as well as checking if the stack is empty. This class leverages LinkedList's functionality to handle stack operations.
